title: ITG2 NoteSkins and fixes
description:
In the zip file is the following:

ITG2 NoteSkins
New ITG2 NoteSkins
Redfix (for if you have the problem of all notes being the same color)
Scrollfix (if the notes aren&#039;t animated, i.e. changing as they move toward the targets)

Directions:

Delete all noteskins in the Noteskins\Dance\ folder INCLUDING default.  Place the new noteskin folders in Noteskins\Dance\.
